322
00:12:43,500 --> 00:12:45,210
You can pluck it out yourself.

323
00:12:45,460 --> 00:12:46,380
Such a trivial matter.

324
00:12:46,980 --> 00:12:47,660
Also,

325
00:12:48,060 --> 00:12:49,100
