394
00:15:58,500 --> 00:15:59,700
Don't talk about it.

395
00:15:59,700 --> 00:16:00,780
Just mentioning it makes me angry.

396
00:16:00,940 --> 00:16:01,820
Meijia and Ye Shu'er

397
00:16:01,820 --> 00:16:03,020
