465
00:18:03,620 --> 00:18:04,260
Yes.

466
00:18:08,380 --> 00:18:09,140
Let go.

467
00:18:10,940 --> 00:18:12,250
I am not Liu Yue,

468
00:18:12,250 --> 00:18:13,780
