526
00:21:09,450 --> 00:21:10,500
You don't have to explain anything,

527
00:21:10,500 --> 00:21:11,540
I am not interested.

528
00:21:12,740 --> 00:21:14,140
How dare a small assistant like you

529
00:21:14,140 --> 00:21:16,260
