559
00:23:04,300 --> 00:23:05,140
I'm fine.

560
00:23:06,060 --> 00:23:07,220
I'm fine.

561
00:23:07,220 --> 00:23:07,780
Don't bother with him.

562
00:23:15,420 --> 00:23:16,100
This child

563
00:23:16,580 --> 00:23:18,500
